sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User (Browser)
    participant WebUI as Web Interface
    participant Auth as Authentication
    participant API as REST API
    participant Queue as Download Queue
    participant Worker as Download Worker
    participant ytdlp as yt-dlp/youtube-dl
    participant WS as WebSocket
    
    User->>WebUI: Access web interface
    WebUI->>Auth: Request login page
    Auth-->>WebUI: Return login form
    User->>Auth: Submit credentials
    Auth->>Auth: Validate credentials
    Auth-->>WebUI: Authentication result
    
    alt Successful login
        WebUI->>WS: Establish WebSocket connection
        WS-->>WebUI: Connection confirmed
        User->>WebUI: Submit download request
        WebUI->>API: POST /download (with auth)
        API->>Queue: Add to queue
        Queue-->>API: Queue position
        API-->>WebUI: Queue status
        WebUI->>WS: Forward status update
        WS-->>User: Real-time update
        
        loop Queue processing
            Worker->>Queue: Get next job
            Queue-->>Worker: Next download task
            Worker->>ytdlp: Execute download
            ytdlp-->>Worker: Download progress
            Worker->>WS: Progress update
            WS-->>User: Real-time progress
            Worker->>ytdlp: Complete download
            ytdlp-->>Worker: Completion status
            Worker->>Queue: Remove completed job
            Worker->>WS: Final status update
            WS-->>User: Download complete
        end
    else Failed login
        Auth-->>WebUI: Error message
        WebUI-->>User: Display error
    end
    
    Note over User,ytdlp: Security: All API calls require authentication
    Note over WebUI,WS: Control Flow: WebSocket maintains real-time connection
    Note over Queue,Worker: Connectivity: Asynchronous queue processing